window.bookSummaryJSON = "In this disturbing, skin-crawling tale of infestation, two roommates find themselves ensnared in the pressure, disgust, and eventual madness of a cockroach invasion. As their lives are taken over within their warm, dark space, we are left with the phantom feeling of bugs swarming everywhere. \"We Found Ourselves Infested\" is a short horror story that can be found in the collection <i>Certain Dark Things</i>, also available on Audible.com."; 
